+### 2. Candidate packet: `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form`
+
+#### Endpoint-exchange memo
+
+- [INFERRED] Native-variable gain, if real:
+  exact decomposition of convection into
+  `(u · ∇)u = ∇(|u|^2/2) - u × ω`,
