+
+- [VERIFIED] Nearest prior-art comparator on the repository record:
+  the mission-level Lamb/Beltrami packet in `MISSION.md`, sharpened by the
+  Step-006 Tao-screen memo for `Lamb-vector / Helmholtz-projected form`.
